snippet.title: Kurmatron -  trailer
snippet.description:
IS IT A UFO? IS IT A TURTLE? IT'S THE KURMATRON! 
An addictive 2D game in pixel art that puts you in control of a ship that fights an evil corporation that is enslaving animals. By abducting them you acquire "animal" powers with the symbiotic technology of Kurmatron.
